  56,45,"'inhm kanuu fi aldunya mtneeimyn balhram, meridyn eamaa ja'athum bih alrsl"
  56,46,"wkanu yuqimun ealaa alkufr biallah wal'ishrak bih wmesyth, wala yanwun altawbat min dhlk"
  56,47,"wkanu yaqulun 'inkarana llbeth: anubeth 'iidha mitna wsrna trabana wezamana baly? whdha aistibead minhum li'amr albaeth wtkdhyb lh"
  56,48,"anubeth nahn wabnawna al'aqdamun aladhin saru trabana, qad tfrraq fi alard?"
  56,49,"ql lahum -ayha alrswl-: 'iina al'awalin walakhirin min bani adam syujmaewn fi yawm muaqat bwqt mhdd, wahu yawm alqyamt"
  56,50,"ql lahum -ayha alrswl-: 'iina al'awalin walakhirin min bani adam syujmaewn fi yawm muaqat bwqt mhdd, wahu yawm alqyamt"